text: Rosalba arawakiana is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Villiers in 1980. It is known from Guadeloupe.BioLib.cz - Rosalba arawakiana. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1980
